metadata.name: Samaness
metadata.description:
This shamaness is a balance of the masculine and feminine.
When the idea of my inner shamaness matured, there was an inner dialogue - reflection...and I heard the voice of my soul.

And the answer instantly appeared in my head "To be happy. To evolve. And kindness."
